e transmitted.\")) (tr (td (a (@ (href \"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/protocol\")) \"`js-websocket-protocol`\")) (td (code \"(extern)\")) (td (code \"(string)\")) (td (code \"(js-websocket-protocol ws)\")) (td \"read the negotiated subprotocol, if any.\")) (tr (td (a (@ (href \"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/extensions\")) \"`js-websocket-extensions`\")) (td (code \"(extern)\")) (td (code \"(string)\")) (td (code \"(js-websocket-extensions ws)\")) (td \"read the negotiated extensions string.\"))))) (h2 (@ (id \"chapter-5--methods\")) \"Chapter 5 — Methods\") (p \"WebSocket API: \" (a (@ (href \"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebSocket\")) \"WebSocket\")) (div (@ (class \"doc-table-wrap\")) (table (thead (tr (th \"Function\") (th \"Input types\") (th \"Output type\") (th \"Example\") (th \"Use when\"))) (tbody (tr (td (a (@ (href \"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/send\")) \"`js-websocket-send`\")) (td (code \"(extern value)\")) (td (code \"()\")) (td (code \"(js-websocket-send ws \\\"hello\\\")\")) (td \"send a message through the socket.\")) (tr (td (a (@ (href \"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/close\")) \"`js-websocket-close`\")) (td (code \"(extern value value)\")) (td (code \"()\")) (td (code \"(js-websocket-close ws 1000 \\\"done\\\")\")) (td \"close the connection, optionally with a code and reason.\"))))) (h2 (@ (id \"chapter-6--mini-workflows\")) \"Chapter 6 — Mini Workflows\") (h3 (@ (id \"build-send-and-inspect-state\")) \"Build, Send, and Inspect State\") (pre (code \"(include-lib websocket)\\n\\n(define ws (websocket-new \\\"wss://example.invalid/socket\\\" (vector \\\"chat\\\")))\\n(websocket-send ws \\\"hello\\\")\\n(websocket-close ws 1000 \\\"done\\\")\\n(list (websocket-url ws)\\n      (websocket-ready-state ws)\\n      (websocket-buffered-amount ws)\\n      (websocket-protocol ws)\\n      (websocket-extensions ws))\")) (h